Package: cards
Title: CDISC Analysis Results Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Daniel D.", "Sjoberg", , "danield.sjoberg@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-0862-2018")),
    person("F. Hoffmann-La Roche AG", role = c("cph", "fnd"))
  )
Description: The package constructs CDISC-compliant Analysis Results Data
    objects. These objects are used (and re-used) to construct summary
    tables, visualizations, and written reports. The results may also be
    represented as JSON or YAML objects.
